        "body": "Fixes #5605\n\n## Description\nThis PR addresses the accessibility issue where navigating between messages was difficult for screen reader users.\nIt replaces the `ScreenReaderText` component with an `<h6>` element in `ActivityRow.tsx`.\nThe `<h6>` element is visually hidden but exposed to the accessibility tree, allowing users to navigate using the 'H' key.\n\n## Changes\n- Modified `packages/component/src/Transcript/ActivityRow.tsx` to use `<h6>`.\n- Added unit test `packages/component/src/Transcript/ActivityRow.spec.tsx`.",
